### Get All Reviews - First Page
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Reviews - Second Page with Custom Limit
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews?page=2&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Reviews - Large Limit
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews?limit=50
Content-Type: application/json

### Get User Reviews (Me) - Requires Authentication
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/me
Content-Type: application/json
# Add your authorization header here
# Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Get User Reviews (Me) - With Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/me?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
# Add your authorization header here
# Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Get Review by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/review_123
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Review by ID - Not Found
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/nonexistent_id
Content-Type: application/json
### Create Review - Requires Authentication
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
# Add your authorization header here
# Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "bookingActivityId": "booking_activity_123",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Amazing experience! The guide was knowledgeable and the activity was well-organized."
}

### Create Review - Minimum Required Fields (Without Comment)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
# Add your authorization header here
# Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "bookingActivityId": "booking_activity_456",
  "rating": 4
}

